Forms.Html: In order to complete the admissions process, we must verify your High School or High School equivalency credentials. This would include a High School Diploma, High School Transcript, or GED documentation. Please scan and upload a copy of one of these documents so that we can continue to process your application for admission. The supported file types are .pdf, .png, .jpg, .docx, .doc, .gif,and .bmp.
